imdb.plot outline: Gwen Lawrence's unique fitness-inspired yoga blends traditional yoga poses with functional strength-training techniques to bring you three 20-minute yoga workouts that guarantee results. Combine the practices for a total-body workout - or use them individually to customize your Fit Body Yoga routine.
